<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>小天才空间站 - 4-7岁空间能力成长地图</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            /* 官方研究建议的黄蓝高对比配色 */
            --primary-yellow: #FFEA7A;
            --shadow-yellow: #D4AF37;
            --primary-blue: #38A9FF;
            --shadow-blue: #2A7EBF;
            --bg-color: #F0F9FF;
            --text-dark: #2D3436;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Fredoka One', 'Arial Rounded MT Bold', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        /* 核心品牌Logo设计：基于红发双辫女孩插画提取 [用户图二] */
       .logo-container {
            margin-top: 40px;
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            border: 8px solid var(--primary-yellow);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 0 var(--primary-blue);
            position: relative;
        }

       .logo-girl-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: #E17055; /* 红发色 */
            mask-image: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12c0 1.25.23 2.45.65 3.55.23.63.78 1.07 1.45 1.07.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5 0-.15-.02-.29-.06-.43-.32-.9-.49-1.87-.49-2.89 0-4.41 3.59-8 8-8s8 3.59 8 8c0 1.02-.17 1.99-.49 2.89-.04.14-.06.28-.06.43 0.83.67 1.5 1.5 1.5.67 0 1.22-.44 1.45-1.07.42-1.1.65-2.3.65-3.55 0-5.52-4.48-10-10-10zM5.5 13c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5S6.33 10 5.5 10 4 10.67 4 11.5s.67 1.5 1.5 1.5zm13 0c.83 0 1.5-.67 1.5-1.5S19.17 10 18.33 10s-1.5.67-1.5 1.5.67 1.5 1.5 1.5z"/></svg>');
            -webkit-mask-image: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="50" cy="45" r="30"/><rect x="15" y="40" width="15" height="40" rx="7"/><rect x="70" y="40" width="15" height="40" rx="7"/></svg>');
            mask-repeat: no-repeat;
            mask-size: contain;
        }

        /* 成长感进度系统 */
       .xp-bar-container {
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 600px;
            height: 30px;
            background: #dfe6e9;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border: 4px solid white;
            box-shadow: inset 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: relative;
        }

       .xp-fill {
            width: 45%; /* 初始进度展示 */
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-blue), #81ecec);
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: width 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
        }

        /* 3D 成长感地图设计 */
       .growth-map {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 60px;
            margin-top: 80px;
            width: 100%;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* 连接关卡的 3D 虚线 */
       .growth-line {
            position: absolute;
            width: 10px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(to bottom, #bdc3c7, #bdc3c7 15px, transparent 15px, transparent 30px);
            height: 80%;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* 三维立体按钮样式 */
       .age-gate {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            width: 280px;
            height: 100px;
            background-color: var(--shadow-blue);
            border-radius: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.1s;
        }

       .age-gate-front {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: var(--primary-blue);
            border-radius: 20px;
            transform: translateY(-8px); /* 初始位移产生厚度感 */
            transition: transform 0.1s, background-color 0.2s;
            border: 4px solid white;
        }

       .age-gate:active.age-gate-front {
            transform: translateY(-2px); /* 点击按下效果 */
        }

       .age-gate.locked.age-gate-front {
            background-color: #b2bec3;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

       .age-gate.yellow-theme { background-color: var(--shadow-yellow); }
       .age-gate.yellow-theme.age-gate-front { background-color: var(--primary-yellow); }

       .age-text {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

       .age-gate.yellow-theme.age-text { color: var(--text-dark); }

       .level-description {
            position: absolute;
            left: 310px;
            width: 200px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

       .badge {
            position: absolute;
            right: -15px;
            top: -15px;
            background: #ff7675;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border: 3px solid white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="logo-container">
        <div class="logo-girl-icon"></div>
    </div>

    <h1>小小空间建筑师</h1>
    <div class="xp-bar-container">
        <div class="xp-fill"></div>
        <div style="position: absolute; top: 40px; width: 100%; text-align: center;">
            距离解锁 6-7岁 挑战还差 200 XP
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="growth-map">
        <div class="growth-line"></div>

        <div class="age-gate" onclick="alert('进入4岁影子匹配模块')">
            <div class="age-gate-front">
                <span class="age-text">4岁：形状感知</span>
                <span class="badge">已达成 ⭐</span>
            </div>
            <div class="level-description">通过旋转三维“重影”匹配物体，建立初步空间感。</div>
        </div>

        <div class="age-gate yellow-theme" onclick="alert('进入5岁迷宫探险模块')">
            <div class="age-gate-front">
                <span class="age-text">5岁：动态路径</span>
                <span class="badge">进行中...</span>
            </div>
            <div class="level-description" style="left: -220px; text-align: right;">切换第一人称视角，训练自我中心坐标转换。</div>
        </div>

        <div class="age-gate locked">
            <div class="age-gate-front">
                <span class="age-text">6-7岁：架构大师</span>
            </div>
            <div class="level-description">将2D蓝图还原为3D建筑。锁定：需达到等级5。</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 进度动态更新模拟
        document.querySelectorAll('.age-gate').forEach(gate => {
            gate.addEventListener('mouseover', () => {
                if(!gate.classList.contains('locked')) {
                    gate.style.transform = 'scale(1.05)';
                }
            });
            gate.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
                gate.style.transform = 'scale(1)';
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
